The old necromancer
In the town of Suslanger lives a necromancer who is trying to prop up Zara's beloved trader as master of the necromancer's guild. If you spoil his experiments, you could gain the trader's gratitude. Material, to be sure.
#subobj 1
Find Kehel's Mansion
The old necromancer's house is located in the northern part of town.
#subobj 2
Revive a corpse with Zara's spell
You can use Zara's scroll to revive a corpse on which the necromancer wanted to perform experiments. As such experiments are forbidden in the city, he will be severely punished.
